2,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"幫巴打推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有啲啲建議 一係比佢痾清哂先 就算痾好多次都可能入面啲菌仲未排哂出嚟<br />\n一係就你睇醫生再拎止痾藥 （但弊處就係如果仲有菌要排出嚟就排唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n一般睇醫生都會比埋調理腸胃既藥你 <br />\n我又覺得可以唔洗睇專科住 我有fd試過痾3日水先開始停 不過佢係睇中醫...<br />\n你試下睇左普通醫生先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下止痾藥幫唔幫到你 加上會附幾隻腸胃藥 睇下o唔ok ？ 我番工見好多人都係咁 （唔好問我番咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁耐都未痾清有D想死, 我聽日會睇下普通醫生, 有人介紹呢個<a href=\"http://www.seedoctor.com.hk/dr_detail-1.asp?dr_doctor=2208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.seedoctor.com.hk%2Fdr_detail-1.asp%3Fdr_doctor%3D2208&d=Y89Ksh3fgoZMo1Q5d7ZfX%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8decd68c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.seedoctor.com.hk/dr_detail-1.asp?dr_doctor=2208</a> 聽朝睇<br />\n<br />\n之前痾水都唔算辛苦, 係依家開始肚痛毛辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我覺得就係上次無排清哂菌, 搞到依家腸胃咁弱"},{"pid":"51f69ba47494e6427687f16f64b0c82f01b0522e","tid":763912,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"我都試過, 屙水屙到真係好似用屎眼屙尿咁<br />\n屙左4日食清左就自己好返, 好後悔無早D睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba5aec7a09b3d9c62ccee3573f6a86036c49316","tid":763912,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f69ba47494e6427687f16f64b0c82f01b0522e","tid":763912,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"我都試過, 屙水屙到真係好似用屎眼屙尿咁<br />\n屙左4日食清左就自己好返, 好後悔無早D睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"我本身就係想等佢自己好, 因為上次都係咁, 但真係太耐都未好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}